How To Install OpenFOAM for the Absolute Beginner

All code can be found at: https://github.com/lordvon/OpenFOAM_Tutorials/tree/master/Installation

DESCRIPTION:
Here we will go over how to install OpenFOAM on Ubuntu Linux.

OUTLINE:
-Follow Instructions on OpenFOAM website.
-Run downloaded scripts.
-Add desired settings.

This tutorial was run successfully on:
-Ubuntu 14.04 64-bit
-OpenFOAM 2.4.0